# JetBrains Toolbox bundled dependencies.
# JetBrains Toolbox has been REMOVED from sandbox-base in this PR, but the
# desktop-x11 PR build still inherits sandbox-base:latest (PRs don't push the
# new base to GHCR — see build.yaml), and :latest still ships JetBrains. Keep
# these waivers until this merges and :latest rolls forward to the JetBrains-free
# base; then they become no-ops and can be pruned (same pattern as the yq block).
