CVE-2022-41404  # ini4j: DoS (bundled in ini4j-0.5.4.jar)
CVE-2026-42583  # netty-codec-compression: Lz4FrameDecoder resource exhaustion (bundled in toolbox.jar)
CVE-2026-42584  # netty-codec-http: HttpClientCodec response desync (bundled in toolbox.jar)
CVE-2026-42587  # netty-codec-http: HttpContentDecompressor maxAllocation bypass (bundled in toolbox.jar)

